<!-- lessons/blind_boolean/views/blind_boolean_form.ejs -->
<div class="flex min-h-screen bg-gray-50 p-4">
  <!-- 왼쪽: 폼 + 힌트 -->
  <main class="w-2/3 pr-4">
    <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-8 space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Boolean-based Blind SQLi 연습</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">참/거짓 조건으로 비밀번호 첫 글자 유추</p>
      <form action="/lesson/blind_boolean/query" method="get" class="space-y-4">
        <div>
          <label for="name" class="block text-gray-700 mb-1">Item Name</label>
          <input
            id="name"
            name="name"
            type="text"
            placeholder="apple 또는 ' AND '1'='1"
            required
            class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:ring focus:border-blue-300"
          />
        </div>
        <button
          type="submit"
          class="w-full py-2 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-md hover:bg-blue-700 transition"
        >
          조회
        </button>
      </form>

      <div class="text-center">
        <button
          id="hint-btn"
          class="px-4 py-2 bg-yellow-400 text-yellow-900 rounded hover:bg-yellow-500 transition"
        >
          힌트 보기
        </button>
      </div>
      <div
        id="hint-box"
        class="hidden p-4 bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-800 rounded text-sm space-y-2"
      >
        <p>▶ 이 쿼리는 사용자가 입력한 이름과 함께 admin 계정 비밀번호 첫 글자를 검사합니다.</p>
        <p>▶ 참이면 해당 아이템이 반환되고, 거짓이면 빈 결과가 됩니다.</p>
        <p>▶ 작은따옴표(`'`)로 문자열을 닫고, <code class="bg-yellow-200 px-1 rounded">AND</code> 뒤에 참/거짓 조건을 추가해 보세요.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <!-- 오른쪽: 실습용 SQL 템플릿 -->
  <aside class="w-1/3 pl-4 sticky top-4">
    <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">실습용 SQL 템플릿</h3>
      <pre class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded text-sm">
SELECT *
FROM items
WHERE name = '&lt;name&gt;'
  AND (
    SELECT substr(password,1,1)
      FROM users
     WHERE username='admin'
  ) = '&lt;char&gt;';
      </pre>
      <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600 text-xs">
        ‘&lt;name&gt;’ 자리에 입력값, ‘&lt;char&gt;’ 자리에 비교할 문자(예: a) 를 넣어 보세요.
      </p>
    </div>
  </aside>
</div>

<script>
  document.getElementById('hint-btn').addEventListener('click', function() {
    const box = document.getElementById('hint-box');
    if (box.classList.contains('hidden')) {
      box.classList.remove('hidden');
      this.textContent = '힌트 숨기기';
    } else {
      box.classList.add('hidden');
      this.textContent = '힌트 보기';
    }
  });
</script>